Rohit ke hoet pehli baar kaale nai safed pade
Tanish aur grishim jinhone bathroom mein make out kiya
Jashan jo boat mein box fek ke aaya
Ritesh jo rohit se better jokes maarta hai
Paras saale ko playground jaane ka ghamand aa gaya hai
Animesh apna nanga avatar
Jagu jiske nukeele samose maine khaye
Aur baaki pyaate actors jinhone humare video mein chaar chand laga diye: piyush,Rocky,Ishaan,dhiraj,Abhishek, Loveya tanish,piyush,sahil, vishal & angad

Production apna bache logo ne bahut acha sambhala lekin sabse badiya jashan, ritesh aur tanni ne samabhala
Becharo ko ek saath bukhar padh gaya
Par ye bukhar ek dusre ko kiss karne ki wajah se aaya

Us bechare ko maine sirf 2 redbull di iss scene ke lie

Editing grishi, ritesh tanni aur kunal ne ki 
Lekin asli haath toh mera hi hota hai huihuihui

And finally sabse zyada special thanks to Sunil Talreja uncle, we love youuu

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

Nikah Episode 45 - [Eng Sub] - Haroon Shahid - Zainab Shabbir - 5th March 2023  - HAR PAL GEO

Nikah is a powerful and inspiring story of a young girl‚Äôs fight for her social and religious rights. 
Opinionated and confident by nature, Anusha is a beautiful young girl who knows how to stand up for her rights. After losing her mother at a young age, Anusha has been brought up by her aunt, Umaima with a lot of love and care. Umamia is a bit hesitant about Anusha‚Äôs assertiveness and often makes her understand. 
Class fellows and best friends, Anusha and Haris are in love with each other and soon plan to marry. On the contrary, Hamdaan is a handsome young man who belongs to a wealthy family and is the only son of his father. He falls in love with Anusha on his very first meeting with her however is respectful of Anusha‚Äôs choices.
Anusha‚Äôs hope and dreams come crashing down when Haris challenges her thoughts. The supposedly liberal fabric of Haris and his family is exposed when Anusha takes a stand for her rights. After losing everything, will Anusha stay true to herself and fight against all odds? Despite everything, will Anusha realize her true admirer and supporter in form of Hamdaan?

Director: Zahid Mehmood

Qalandar is a story of a girl‚Äôs firm belief in her God and His decisions while the rest of the world continues to hurt, defame and challenge her.

Dur-e-Adan is a young and innocent girl who has grown up under the care of her uncle and aunt. Despite being an orphan at an early age, Dur-e-Adan doesn‚Äôt complain about her challenges and difficulties.

snippet.title: ‡Æá‡Æü‡Æø‡ÆØ‡Ææ‡Æ™‡Øç‡Æ™ ‡ÆÖ‡Æö‡Øç‡Æö‡Æø ‡Æ™‡Øã‡Æ§‡ØÅ‡ÆÆ‡Øç ! ‡ÆØ‡Ææ‡Æ∞‡Øç ‡Æµ‡Øá‡Æ£‡Ææ‡Æ≤‡ØÅ‡ÆÆ‡Øç ‡Æà‡Æ∏‡Æø‡ÆØ‡Ææ‡Æï ‡Æ™‡Æ∞‡Øã‡Æü‡Øç‡Æü‡Ææ ‡Æö‡ØÜ‡ÆØ‡Øç‡ÆØ‡Æ≤‡Ææ‡ÆÆ‡Øç | Easy Parrota Recipe Tamil | parotta
snippet.description:
#parottarecipeintamil, #layerparottaintamil #parotta

Easy Method of  Parotta making

350gram of Maida flour in the Bowl 
Add required salt ,one spoon oil and mixed well
Adding Boiled water little by little mixed well
make dough chapati consistency.
take idiyappam Achu and filled this batter 3/4
three spoons of cooking oil Grease with plate
make parotta peda shown in the video

cover it Rest in 15mins to 30mins
apply oil in top of peda
then gentle press  make parotta
 cooking parotta in the medium flame
Now your layered parotta is ready..

Easy Method of  Parotta making

350gram of Maida flour in the Bowl 
Add required salt ,one spoon oil and mixed well
Adding Boiled water little by little mixed well
make dough chapati consistency.
take idiyappam Achu and filled this batter 3/4
three spoons of cooking oil Grease with plate
make parotta peda shown in the video

cover it Rest in 15mins to 30mins
apply oil in top of peda
then gentle press  make parotta
 cooking parotta in the medium flame
Now your layered parotta is ready..

snippet.title: Nadiya Ke Paar Funny Scene | Best Scene Of Nadiya Ke Paar | Holi Special | Sachin Pilgaonkar
snippet.description:
Checkout this Classic Scene from the Classic Movie "Nadiya Ke Paar" released in the year 1982. Starring Sachin Pilgaonkar, Sadhana Singh, Inder Thakur, Savita Bajaj, Sheela David. Watch such classic scene only on @Rajshri 

#nadiyakepaar #bollywoodmovies #romanticmovie 

Synopsis-
The story is based on the first half of a Hindi novel, Kohbar Ki Shart by Keshav Prasad Mishra. A Brahman farmer from Eastern Uttar Pradesh lives with his two nephews. He falls ill and is treated by a Vaidya (indigenous medical practitioner) from another village. When the farmer feels okay, he asks the Vaidya about his fees. The Vaidya asks for the farmer's eldest nephew to marry his eldest daughter. The farmer readily agrees.

Omkar marries the Vaidya's elder daughter Roopa, and they start living happily. Roopa gives birth to a baby. During Roopa's pregnancy, her younger sister Gunja comes to live with her. While there, she falls in love with Omkar's younger brother Chandan.

Learning of their love, Roopa promises to help them marry. But, she dies in an accident; and nobody else knows about the love affair. The farmer and the Vaidya decide that Gunja should marry the widower Omkar, to take care of her sister's baby. But moments before the wedding rituals are completed, Chandan and Gunja's love affair is revealed. He is allowed to marry Gunja with everyone's consent.

The rural culture and languages of Uttar Pradesh are portrayed authentically in the film. The movie is based on the first half of the novel. It changes the partners in the second marriage, as the novel had the proposed marriage between Gunja and Omkar taking place. The novel proceeded with the development of their relationship, where Omkar dies of illness and eventually Gunja also dies leaving Chandan alone.

snippet.description:
Star Studios presents in association with Dharma Productions, Prithviraj Productions, Magic Frames & Cape Of Good Films.
A Dharma Productions Film SELFIEE
Starring Akshay Kumar, Emraan Hashmi, Nushrratt Bharuccha, Diana Penty
Directed by Raj Mehta
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Aruna Bhatia, Supriya Menon, Karan Johar, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Apoorva Mehta & Listin Stephen

Song : Deewaane 
Singer : Aditya Yadav, Stebin Ben, Altamash Faridi
Original Composer : Aditya Yadav
Recreated by : Tanishk Bagchi
Programmed and arranged by : Tanishk Bagchi
New Lyrics : Kunaal Vermaa 
Original Lyrics : Aditya Yadav

DOP : Shinda Singh
Choreographer : Adil Shaikh
Strings : Mert Kemanci

PlayDMF team - Gaurav Arora , Asheema Chauhan & Sankalp Garg 
Special thanks - Rajat Nagpal
Digital Promotions - Underdog Digital 
YouTube Promotions - Net Media

Lyrics

Mazaa aa jaata hai
Adhoori baaton se
Koi mann jaata hai
Zaroori yaaron se
Jo dekhi na suni aisi
Hume duniya dikhati hai
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

Nazar aati hain zulfon mein
Ghataein badalon jaisi
Yeh dil karne laga unse
Wafaein paglon jaisi
Usse jab dekhte hain toh
Badal jaata hai yeh lehza
Zubaan pe aa hi jaati hai
Adayein shayaron jaisi
Unhe jab yaad karte hain
Tabhi barsaat aati hai
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

Nahin koi gila humein
Jo na iss baar maanenge
Abhi chahe mana kar de
Kabhi toh yaar maanenge
Miley jo cheez aasani se 
Toh usme mazaa kaisa
Unhe mera banana tak
Na hum bhi haar maanenge
Suna hai chahatein sachi
Nahin barbaad jaati hain
Deewaane hum nahin hote
Deewaani raat aati hai 
Hume unki uhne meri
Mohabbat yaad aati hai

#akshaykumar #emraanhashmi #jacquelinefernandez

Puranpoli | ‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£‡§™‡•ã‡§≥‡•Ä ‚Äì 
‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£ ‡§¨‡§®‡§µ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making Puran
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§∞‡§≠‡§∞‡§æ ‡§°‡§æ‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Bengal Gram 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§≥‡§¶ ¬º tsp | Turmeric ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | Oil 2 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä | Water 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡•Ç‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Jaggery 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§µ‡•á‡§≤‡§ö‡•Ä ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Cardamom pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§Ø‡§´‡§≥ ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Nutmeg pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡•Å‡§Ç‡§† ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ‡•ß/‡•™ tsp | Ginger pw 1/4 tsp
‡§ï‡§£‡§ø‡§ï ‡§Æ‡§≥‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making dough 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§™‡•Ä‡§† 4 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Wheat flour 4 cups
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§Æ‡•Ä‡§† ¬Ω tsp | Salt to taste
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2-3 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | oil 2-3 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä ‡§ó‡§∞‡§ú‡•á‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞ | Water as required

Method ‚Äì
 ‚Ä¢ For making dough in a wheat flour add salt and knead the dough, rest for 20 mins and then apply some oil and knead soft dough again.
 ‚Ä¢ Wash and soak chana daal for about 30 minutes. 
 ‚Ä¢ Heat up water in a pressure cooker, add soaked daal along with water, add turmeric and oil and take 4-5 whistles on med heat.
 ‚Ä¢ Once cooked, separate daal and water. 
 ‚Ä¢ Once daal is at room temp, grind into mixer grinder.
 ‚Ä¢ Now add ground daal into a kadhai, add chopped jaggery and turn on the gas flame.
 ‚Ä¢ Now saute till mixture gets thickness then add cardamom and nutmeg powder.
 ‚Ä¢ Then turn off the heat and let the puran cool down completely. 
 ‚Ä¢ Now take ball size dough, dust some rice flour and fill the equal amount of puran and roll roti / puranpoli . dust rice flour whenever required,
 ‚Ä¢ Roast the puranpoli, apply ghee or oil.

Puranpoli | ‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£‡§™‡•ã‡§≥‡•Ä ‚Äì 
‡§™‡•Å‡§∞‡§£ ‡§¨‡§®‡§µ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making Puran
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§∞‡§≠‡§∞‡§æ ‡§°‡§æ‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Bengal Gram 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§π‡§≥‡§¶ ¬º tsp | Turmeric ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | Oil 2 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä | Water 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡•Ç‡§≥ 2 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Jaggery 2 Cup
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§µ‡•á‡§≤‡§ö‡•Ä ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Cardamom pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§Ø‡§´‡§≥ ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ¬º tsp | Nutmeg pw ¬º tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§∏‡•Å‡§Ç‡§† ‡§™‡•Ç‡§° ‡•ß/‡•™ tsp | Ginger pw 1/4 tsp
‡§ï‡§£‡§ø‡§ï ‡§Æ‡§≥‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä | For making dough 
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§ó‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ‡§ö‡•á ‡§™‡•Ä‡§† 4 ‡§µ‡§æ‡§ü‡•Ä | Wheat flour 4 cups
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§Æ‡•Ä‡§† ¬Ω tsp | Salt to taste
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§§‡•á‡§≤ 2-3 ‡§ö‡§Æ‡§ö‡•á | oil 2-3 tsp
 ‚Ä¢ ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä ‡§ó‡§∞‡§ú‡•á‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞ | Water as required

Method ‚Äì
 ‚Ä¢ For making dough in a wheat flour add salt and knead the dough, rest for 20 mins and then apply some oil and knead soft dough again.
 ‚Ä¢ Wash and soak chana daal for about 30 minutes. 
 ‚Ä¢ Heat up water in a pressure cooker, add soaked daal along with water, add turmeric and oil and take 4-5 whistles on med heat.
 ‚Ä¢ Once cooked, separate daal and water. 
 ‚Ä¢ Once daal is at room temp, grind into mixer grinder.
 ‚Ä¢ Now add ground daal into a kadhai, add chopped jaggery and turn on the gas flame.
 ‚Ä¢ Now saute till mixture gets thickness then add cardamom and nutmeg powder.
 ‚Ä¢ Then turn off the heat and let the puran cool down completely. 
 ‚Ä¢ Now take ball size dough, dust some rice flour and fill the equal amount of puran and roll roti / puranpoli . dust rice flour whenever required,
 ‚Ä¢ Roast the puranpoli, apply ghee or oil.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3711 - 6 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3711: Holi Ki Taiyyari
--------------------------------------------------------
With Holi just around the corner, Tapu Sena surprises Sonu with some color. Despite Sonu's enthusiasm, Tapu Sena is told to save their elation for the celebration. His wife questions Sodhi about his "party sharty," but Bhide manages to spare him. Tapu Sena visits Bhide's home later. They paint everyone, but Bhide chastises them for painting the inside of the house; however, Madhavi let them because it is festival season. Tapu Sena has a novel way to celebrate Holi this year, which everyone is excited to know. What new concept does Tapu Sena have this time? Follow along!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3711, 6 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: DKL | Tanzeel Khan
snippet.description:
#DKL #Dillikiladki #TanzeelKhan 

Been a while since I last shared some of my music with the world, 6months to be precise, couldn‚Äôt have thought of a better restart than #DKL a complete new single
Which we composed, wrote , dubbed , shot and edited in just 4 days time .
A song me and my friends and family love is good enough to make you feel nostalgic and remind you of my very first song #DilliKiLadki that dropped on this exact date 3 years ago.

Hope y‚Äôall like and enjoy this one
Dont forget to like the video, listen to it,share with your friends and give me yout feedback‚ô•Ô∏è
Lots of love meri public ü´∂üèª
Here we go again!

Written, Co-composed, Sung and Directed by Tanzeel Khan

Audio:
Written, composed and performed by Tanzeel Khan
Song Composed by Akarsh Shetty & Bibhash Buragohain
Music Arranged and Produced by Akarsh Shetty
Guitars by Bibhash Buragohain
Song Mixed by Akarsh Shetty
Song Mastered by Hanish Taneja

Video:
Executive Producer- Dane Pereira
DOP - Arun Sharma, Abhishek Kini
Edit & DI Colourist- Abhishek Kini
Artwork - Darsh Nishar

Special Thanks : Vaibhav Patil

Team Believe Artist Services: Shilpa Sharda, Akshay Kapoor

For Licensing enquiries : sync-india@believedigital.com

For Artist Enquires contact : dane.pereira@nofiltr.social

Lyrics :-
Dekha chehra tera aaj bhi
Lagta gehra yeh raaz hi
Sochu tujhko mein harjagah ,hardafa-hardafa

mein kehraha hu yeh baat hi
Mere shaamon ki tu raat si
sab yaar hai par tu khaas si,kyu lage -kyu lage

Dhalne lagi hai shaam bhi
Mein neend aur tu khwab si
Chahta hai dil yeh  har ghadi/aaj bhi
Ki teri baahon mein rahe


Karti tu mujhpe jaadugari
Hoti tu jab jab saath khadi_mere_
Dilli ki ladki hai dil mein basi.. wohh oh

Jannat se utri tu jaise pari 
Nashe si tu ab sar chadi mere
Dilli ki ladki hai dil mein basi.. wohh ohh

Paas bulaye ,teri adaayein
Karke beimaniyan
Raaton ko jaage, koi na jaane
Kya hamare darmiyaan

Teri aankhein,teri baatein
na hai koi khaamiyan
Dekhe taare kaafi saare
tujh sa na koi mila

Na hai dhali yeh raat bhi
Mein kyu chakhu sharaab bhi
Karde mujhe kharaab hi
Yeh teri aankhon ke nashee‚Ä¶eee..


Karti tu mujhpe jaadugari
Hoti tu jab jab saath khadi_mere_
Dilli ki ladki hai dil mein basi.. wohh oh

Jannat se utri tu jaise pari 
Nashe si tu ab sar chadi mere
Dilli ki ladki hai dil mein basi.. wohh ohh

snippet.title: Sunday Brunch With Venkatesh Daggubati & Rana Daggubati X Kamiya Jani | Ep 96 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
We have two of the biggest South superstars on the show this time -  the uncle-nephew duo, Venkatesh Daggubati & Rana Daggubati. 

Now Mumbai cannot match up to Hyderabadi food so we treated them with what Mumbai is known for - Mumbaiya street food & chaat at Hitchki, BKC in Mumbai. Candidly, they spoke to us about their journeys, working in Bollywood & Telugu film industry, the food they like to eat, and a lot more. 

We played a fun game of, ‚ÄòHow Well Do You Know Each Other?‚Äô And surprisingly their answers were bang on. Watch to know more!  

Watch the entire episode and let us know in the comment section below which southern superstar should we call next on our show?

snippet.description:
Weekly ReLIV is a special compilation of the week‚Äôs episodes and is created to give the viewer a feel of the show‚Äôs story and it‚Äôs high points. The weekly ReLIV here is created especially for the viewers who have missed the week‚Äôs episodes and would like to catch up on the plot of their favorite shows. Watch the Weekly ReLIV of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah of the episodes from 27 February 2023 To 4 March 2023.

Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Raj Anadkat, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: (3705 - 3710) 27 February 2023 To 4 March 2023
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah 
#SAB 
#‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ 

Click here to Subscribe to Sony SAB: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the Weekly Reliv episodes: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7aq_DUPLxBkU49WEPPcecgS

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3710 - 4 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3710: Jethalal Ka Promise
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha scares himself by daydreaming about going bald in Gokuldham. He imagines everyone laughing at him while Babita refuses to help. As he wakes up from his imagination, he sees Nattu and Bagha who have bought "jalebi fafda" for him. Jetha refuses to eat it and decides to run away. He is stopped by Babita and Iyer at the door and comes back inside the shop to tell them the truth. Iyer is angry while Babita is left shocked as Jethalal tries to tell the whole story. Watch the episode to know more.
 
Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3710, 4 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Every Indian During Holi | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys , 
This Holi Video has every Holi situation we experience. How Indians celebrate holi . The crazy masti of Holi . Revenge wali holi , pyaar wali holi , dosto ke sath , holi fest ki holi , college wali holi , holi pool party , exams wali holi . During board exams skipping holi festival and studying whole day , Indian mom scoulding and letting go out tom play holi with friends on streets with water ballons , pichkari , herbal colors and forcing to go to tuition on Holi , deciding holi songs playlist , grooving on ap dhillon songs , enjoying bhang thandai , beer , gol gappe , dahi bhalle , gujia sweets , getting gifts from relatives gulal , rang , all the colors , pichkari , desi ghee gujia , hugging enemies sorting out the grudges , hitting with water balloons , water guns , dancing , enjoying holika dhayan , the festival of colors . Girls planning to go parlour after holi so that holi colours comes out with waxing , facial , eyebrow threading , while girl got her periods and is avoiding holi cause she can't deal with tampons , menstrual cups and pads . After marraige first holi , lakde wale in lakdi walo ke ghar , making dahi bhalle , dancing , colouring the newlyweds , new couple having their romantic holi in front of in laws , mother in law and father in law , devar , devrani , jethani , nanad all in Mom house . Planning to go out to celebrate holi with big group travelling in train bus to vrindavan , brij ki holi , jaipur , udaipur holi , mathura holi foreigners wali Holi . Society ki holi party with all the food stalls , rang , gujia , gol gappe , sweets , pickari , chandhan , bhang , kulfi . Ladies dressing like Hema malini , Rekha white suit , bandni duppata , doing holi fashion in indian traditional wear , buying Ready made gobar uple . Packing holi Gifts for Indian relatives , kids buying water guns every holi , asking more colours , discussing kodda holi of haryana . School friends deciding to play after school in school corridoor , Hiding colour packets in school bag to play holi with school friends , ruining school uniform with colours , mummy scoulding  . Chintu Chinki Bhai Behen after holi in stained holi colours Mom savitri feeding cold puri , thandi puri achar , sabzi , and tea , after bathing multiple times to get the color out , Indian family getting to bed to sleep , plans to eat faluda kulfiin the evening enjoying with a good movie . Brother going out with his bro friends again playing holi with grease . Sister telling Mom , and mom daughter freaking out  . Taking out revenge by applying colours, the foodies, getting painted first by the bf/gf, mixing pakka color into herbal colors, balloon horror created in society that we go through in holi days, and The Best Holi Fight between two groups.. Well you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 
Do Share it with everyone, Comment your fav part and like krdena Video guys.. Subscribe the Channel for more amazing videos . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family  .. Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and  

Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Tena Jaiin : https://www.instagram.com/tenajaiin/?...
